      <title>美国抛售 1800 亿美元国债，高收益吸引买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/treasuries-hold-loses-after-solid-demand-for-record-us-five-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国政府本周向市场注入超过 1,800 亿美元的新债，美国国债需求保持坚挺，这证明了短期债券高收益率的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/treasuries-hold-loses-after-solid-demand-for-record-us-five-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 17:10:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
